<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524432>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–5. Caenohomalopoda shikokuensis (Tachikawa), holotype, female.3, habitus, dorsal; 4, habitus, lateral; 5, holotype ticket indicating data. (Photographs by Mr. Taisuke Kawano, and reproduced with permission of Dr. Mita)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524432/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524434>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–12. Caenohomalopoda shikokuensis (Tachikawa), female, Indian specimen. 6, head frontal; 7, mandible; 8, antenna; 9, fore wing; 10, mesosoma; 11, scutellum; 12, gaster showing ovipositor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524434/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524444>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35–43. Caenohomalopoda koreana Tachikawa, Paik & Paik. (35–41) female: 35, head frontal; 36, mandible; 37, antenna; 38, fore wing; 39, fore wing, distal venation, enlarged; 40, scutellum; 41, metasoma. (42,43) male: 42, antenna; 43, fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524444/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524430>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1, 2. Caenohomalopoda albifuniculata Hayat, holotype, female. 1, antenna; 2, fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524438>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–25. Caenohomalopoda longistylata Singh. (21–22) female. 21, habitus holotype, dorsal; 22, head, mesosoma and part of gaster, dorsal holotype. (23–25, paratype) 23, antenna; 24, fore wing; 25, ovipositor. (Reproduced with permission of Dr. S. Singh)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524438/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524436>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–20. Caenohomalopoda sudhiri sp. nov., holotype, female. 13, head frontal; 14, mandible; 15, antenna; 16, fore wing; 17, fore wing, distal venation, enlarged; 18, mesosoma; 19, scutellum; 20, gaster showing ovipositor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524436/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524442>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–34. Caenohomalopoda tahai Fatima & Zeya, holotype, female. 32, habitus; 33, antenna; 34, fore wing. (From Fatima & Zeya, 2017)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524442/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524448>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47–51. Caenohomalopoda longiclava Basha & Hayat. (47–49) paratype, female. 47, antenna; 48, fore wing; 49, fore wing, distal venation, enlarged. (50,51) holotype, male: 50, antenna; 51, fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524448/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6524440>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–31. Caenohomalopoda heera Hayat & F. R. Khan, holotype, female, 26, head; 27, antenna; 28, fore wing; 29, fore wing, distal venation, enlarged; 30, scutellum; 31, mesosoma and metasoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6524440/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

